                <h4 data-uuid="61d9af680ca746ff96df785a978ed77b">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="a039cf0c1e724c2a9140e4263ca2530e">Citizenship in the United States is determined
                    in several ways.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="5de6e5a87621422f90e786550efa3d7a">Gaining
                    U.S. Citizenship</h2>
                <div class="yellow-star-yellow-bar" data-uuid="479c9337e577488697c41be0051df4c3"></div>
            </article>
        </section>
